/target
.claude
.worktrees
/.secrets

# .github/secrets/ accepts only age-encrypted blobs and the recipients/README
# files. Everything else (stray .p12, .jks, plaintext .env, decrypt leftovers)
# stays untracked to prevent accidental commits of plaintext secrets.
/.github/secrets/*
!/.github/secrets/*.age
!/.github/secrets/recipients.txt
!/.github/secrets/README.md
